latestIgtvVideos.title: Birthday Post (1/2)
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey y'all,
Everytime I promise that I'll be regular on the gram but then life just happens 🙈
Anyway, cutting to the chase,
A week back I had my birthday and let me tell you it was one of the best that I've ever had. I wanted to celebrate this day with some of my very close friends away from the clutches of our usual tiring lives and hence went for @jashnresortlko
And let me tell you, in the least exaggerating way possible, that every aspect of my stay here exceeded my expectations. 
They were such a great host. Starting from the decorations to keeping in mind all our needs, be it any time of the day, they were on their toes. 
With such great staff, amazing location, delicious food and inexplicable services, my stay here not just made my weekends better but also added great fun to my birthday. 
I would highly recommend this place to people who are willing to just get away from their monotonous lives and have a chill vibe, cause trust me, the vibe here is tranquilizing! 
.
.
.
Also, Thank you guys madhukant_tripathi @lustfor.lifee @shantanu_maharani @nutrifit_advisor @apekshyashrestha100 for making my day really fun. 
And I really missed you guys @bellaisha_16
@the_styleup_chic @_l.a_reina @diksarora11@harley__007 @_bhavika.786 @thatblacklashgirl 🥺
Lastly, Stay tuned for more pictures and videos. Will be posting a lot new content in the coming week! 
Excited already!!!!!!!!!!!! 🤩
